<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dignity-n">dignity <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'dɪɡnəti/    美 /'dɪɡnəti/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>尊贵；尊严：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The real dignity of a man lies in what he is, not in what he has. 
一个人真正的尊严在于他的品格，而非他的财富。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>庄严；端庄：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ladies and gentlemen should always act <strong>with</strong> great <strong>dignity</strong>. 
绅士、淑女应该始终保持端庄得体的举止。</p></div></div>